Hey everyone! 🚀

I’m really excited to share the **first release of our desktop application – Voice Mode Agent** 🎤💻

After a lot of development and iterations, it’s now available as a **fully installable desktop app** (no setup required). You can simply download, install, and start using it right away.

### 🔽 How to get started:

1. Download the **.zip file** shared in this channel
2. Extract it
3. Run the **Voice Mode Agent Setup (.exe)** file
4. If Windows shows a warning, click **“More Info → Run Anyway”**
5. Install and launch the app 🎉

That’s it — the app will handle everything (including backend) automatically in the background.

Would love for you all to try it out and share your feedback 🙌
Really looking forward to hearing your thoughts!
